title: YAWOBFR!
body:
A guy named codeadict created a

small web-app
, dedicated to my repacks. In other words, it’s

Yet Another Way Of Browsing FitGirl Repacks!

Or, in terms of the creator, Catalog.

 
 
http://codeadict.pythonanywhere.com/

Nice stats available too. Use it when my list or search is not enough.

Kudos to codeadict!
